Starts battle in <Standby> and does not attack; After being injured, this unit becomes <Combat-Ready>, gradually losing HP over time and continually inflicting <@eb.key>Nervous Impairment</> to nearby units.
Takes up <@eb.key>2 Blocks</>; Gradually <@eb.key>accelerates</> when charging, dealing damage based on <@eb.key>Movement Speed</> to any target it passes through or is blocked by.
